<para id="fs-id1169594034174">Notice, in <link target-id="CNX_ElemAlg_Figure_04_02_040"/>, the equation <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mi>x</m:mi></m:mrow></m:math> gives a slanted line, while <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>y</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> gives a horizontal line.</para>
